## Additional Terms for Islamic Content

This software contains Islamic religious content including Quranic verses, 
Hadith, and other religious texts. Users are requested to:

1. Handle all Islamic content with respect and care
2. Ensure proper attribution when sharing or redistributing content
3. Verify religious content with qualified Islamic scholars
4. Use this application to support and enhance Islamic practice

## Third-Party Content

This application integrates with various APIs and services:
- Aladhan API for prayer times
- Quran API for Quranic text and translations  
- Hadith API for authentic Hadith collections
- Firebase services for backend functionality

Please refer to their respective terms of service and licenses.

## Disclaimer

This application is intended for educational and religious purposes. 
While every effort has been made to ensure accuracy of religious content,
users should always consult with qualified Islamic scholars for religious
guidance and verification of information.

